OL,5, The price of a pint of beer will have  
OL,6, to rise by as much as 30p to help pay  
OL,7, for higher wages and energy costs, one 
OL,8, pub owner has warned.                  
OL,10,FAs the government prepares to unveil   
OL,11,Fits Budget, City Pub Group said price  
OL,12,Frises were "the only way forward".     
OL,14,FOn Monday, the government said the     
OL,15,FNational Living Wage would rise to     
OL,16,F#9.50 per hour in April for those over 
OL,17,F23 years old.                          
OL,19,FClive Watson, the chain's boss, said   
OL,20,Fthis would cost it about #1m a year.   
